display_long_description:
# Medooval Knight Update ⚔️🐴🛡️🏰🍌

**Raise thy banana and prepare for glory in the latest Monkey Doo update!**

The Medooval Knight Update has arrived—time to gear up and hop on your noble steed

**New Sweet Dealz**

Royal jesters have stocked Sweet Dealz island for April Fools

**Medooval Battle Pass**

Suit up for battle with medieval-themed cosmetics, including the Knight Helmet, Knight Mask, Knight Shield, Knight Sword, and Breastplate

**Noble Steed Bundle**

Gallop into chaos with the all-new cosmetic

**New Variant**

New Croc Hat—designed by the community

[media]

================================================

**About**
# Live in the heart of the Bermuda Triangle with all your Monkey friends! Swing on vines, throw doo at your enemies, and climb everything! 

- Huge Maps: Explore the Bermuda Jungle, Floating Forests, Ancient Ruins, Lava Chasm, and more

- Unique Gamemodes: Be the first to collect 10 bananas or work together to fend off hordes of crocs -- new modes are coming all the time

- Monkey Apparel: Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo

- Ruby Mines: Explore a seemingly endless set of tunnels filled with lore, new NPC's, and our Battle Pass! Unlock exclusive rewards like Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more with free and paid rewards! 

Jump into the recently installed mining elevator to descend deep into the old ruby mines. Survive the **wrath of Xongo & save the Lost Souls** in Monkey Doo's all new Horror Mode!
